  "title": "WAREHOUSE MANAGER",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>Responsibilities and Duties</strong></em></p><p><p><p>* Manage day-to-day warehouse operations including inbound, storage, picking, packing, dispatch, and returns.</p><p>* Oversee e-commerce fulfilment operations to ensure accuracy, speed, and service level adherence.</p><p>* Lead onboarding and setup of new warehouse clients and fulfilment businesses.</p><p>* Plan and optimize warehouse layout, manpower, workflows, and inventory processes.</p><p>* Ensure uninterrupted warehouse operations with proper capacity planning and contingency management.</p><p>* Monitor inventory accuracy, stock movements, and reconciliation.</p><p>* Implement and maintain standard operating procedures (SOPs), safety standards, and compliance requirements.</p><p>* Coordinate with internal teams, transport partners, and last-mile delivery providers.<br /><br />* Other duties as assigned.</p></p></p><p><em><strong>Knowledge and Skills Requirement</strong></em></p><p>* Degree in Logistics/ Supply Chain Management.<br />* Minimum 5 years’ experience in Operational, Logistics background and People Management.<br />* Strong leadership, management and problem-solving skills.<br />* Driving licence required.<br />* Ability to work in a fast-paced, high-volume operational environment.</p>",
